Complete front-end system for a student accommodation listing website using Html, CSS, JavaScript.
It includes:
1. Clean homepage displaying featured accommodation listings
2. Listings Page showing all available houses and rooms, with a sidebar that allows students to search and filter with their preferences.
3. A detailed view page for each listing (images, price, location and description).
4. A contact page that allows students to send messages through the web or use an email.

App.js - CampusStay front-end
Single-file SPA using hash routing (#/ , #/listings, #/listing/:id, #/contact)

Features implemented:
1. Data array of listings (images, price, distance, rooms, type)
2. Render home (featured), listings with search and filters, detail view
3. Save favorites in localStorage
4. Search, filter, sort functionality
5. Mobile menu toggle